{"tid":1009071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[環保撚] 有熟食檔重用蠔殼售賣　陳肇始疑講錯：全力支持環保","createTime":"2019-02-05T02:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T04:47:34.000Z","uid":26602,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d487f6ab46c4aeb5a41ff0e1cf1245e22879945","tid":1009071,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"踏入大年初一，年宵市場的攤檔都收拾好準備回家過年。今早（5日）行政長官林鄭月娥及食物及衛生局局長陳肇始就到維園探訪清潔工，又派柑感謝他們工作辛勞。<br />\n<br />\n然而未知是否太早出動，陳肇始在回答問題時卻「答錯題」；被問到是否得悉有人重用蠔殼當生蠔賣，陳肇始卻回應「全力支持環保」，在記者再追問時才回應：「每一個攤檔都必須遵循食環署提供的指引」。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始今早與特首林鄭月娥到維園探望清潔工後見記者，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">途中有記者及到是否知悉有人循環再用蠔殼，以及有否收到投訴及食物中毒的個案；惟其時陳肇始疑似聽錯問題，以為是問到年宵市場的環保及清潔問題。她回應指，相信市民對如何在年宵市場源頭減廢、提高環保意識有很多的意見，食環署及環保局一直有保持密切溝通，強調兩局「全力支持環保」。又希望市民有環保意識，令年宵市場的環保情況變得更好。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n攤檔必須遵循食環署提供的指引<br />\n<br />\n其後有記者再次重覆有攤檔重用蠔殼的問題，陳肇始才恍然大悟，僅回應指，每一個攤檔都必須遵循食環署提供的指引；其後就未有回答問題離去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/291777/%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B42019-%E6%9C%89%E7%86%9F%E9%A3%9F%E6%AA%94%E9%87%8D%E7%94%A8%E8%A0%94%E6%AE%BC%E5%94%AE%E8%B3%A3-%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%E7%96%91%E8%AC%9B%E9%8C%AF-%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F291777%2F%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B42019-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2586%259F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%25AA%2594%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25A0%2594%25E6%25AE%25BC%25E5%2594%25AE%25E8%25B3%25A3-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25AC%259B%25E9%258C%25AF-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=b3042997\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/291777/%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B42019-%E6%9C%89%E7%86%9F%E9%A3%9F%E6%AA%94%E9%87%8D%E7%94%A8%E8%A0%94%E6%AE%BC%E5%94%AE%E8%B3%A3-%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%E7%96%91%E8%AC%9B%E9%8C%AF-%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D</a>"},{"pid":"ff53b3cdb9ffd9d04df306d519fb0d418a6e72aa","tid":1009071,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"其實有無人報過海關<br />\n最起碼商品說明條例都有刑事後果  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deef667abb359498b4774ac542747221f68f6dc1","tid":1009071,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f12ad532277b87751480f07e26a2dced675d221","tid":1009071,"uid":28831,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ff53b3cdb9ffd9d04df306d519fb0d418a6e72aa","tid":1009071,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"其實有無人報過海關<br />\n最起碼商品說明條例都有刑事後果  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"支那蝗你覺得政府會做嘢？"},{"pid":"305cf1d3aff40a6dba210eb2bbd09185c133367d","tid":1009071,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"全力反對食物衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8bbd2d43d33643e87fc396cbaae5a7239d8ee1","tid":1009071,"uid":46973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:13:29.000Z","msg":"原本啲蠔都有殼，邊到環保，用咁多水洗未仲唔環保，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b58b0f9e977b635f1acf47fae8372bc311abdf","tid":1009071,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"弱撚智<br />\n不如屙完屎自己食返最撚環保"},{"pid":"0d31eca9bdca8558a5d336d238b681b947ee2672","tid":1009071,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s